# UGC Ad Creator API - HTTP Requests
# Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3000/health

### API Information
GET http://localhost:3000/api

### Generate UGC Ad - Basic Example
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ugc/generate
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="creativeBrief"

Create an engaging fitness app advertisement showcasing workout tracking features and motivating users to stay active
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="fitness-app.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-images/fitness-app.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

