### Generate UGC Ad - With Custom Options
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ugc/generate
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW

------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="creativeBrief"

Create a vertical social media advertisement for a fitness app targeting young adults
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="options"

{
  "aspectRatio": "9:16",
  "segmentCount": 1,
  "useFastModel": true,
  "personGeneration": "allow_adult"
}
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="images"; filename="vertical-content.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./sample-images/vertical-content.jpg
------WebKitFormBoundary7MA4YWxkTrZu0gW--

### Check Generation Status
GET http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ugc/status/ugc_1705312200_abc123def

### Download Videos
POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/ugc/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "operationId": "ugc_1705312200_abc123def"
}

